{"tid":431051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑日報：【犯我波子，雖遠必誅】","createTime":"2017-10-10T10:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T01:37:14.000Z","uid":70985,"like":389,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9b1e28ed6086c06d9217c7109c075d84b44735","tid":431051,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【犯我波子，雖遠必誅】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一間藥房日日人來人往，顧客與貓，相安無事，「波子」個個都唔 Wea，淨係 Wea 你個仔，愛動物的人都知道，一隻小貓不是獅子，唔係個逆子出手攻擊、滋擾、挑釁在先，波子會出手？<br />\n一件屁事，竟然浪費到：1，警方重案組、2，醫務處白車及救護人員、3，漁護處人員，特區政府三大部門，同你個衰仔出頭？<br />\n簡直笑話。<br />\n我也是納稅人，我對那個小孩會否染上瘋狗症毫無興趣，我只想問一下即將發表簡短版派錢「施政報告」的林鄭，你都知道王大媽的纏腳布，又長又煩，王大媽式小事化大的胡鬧喧嘩「投訴」，全世界更神憎鬼厭&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n請問林鄭：香港納稅人的公帑，是否無休無止可以為這種無聊笑話長開水喉、資源浪費？<br />\n美國文豪馬克吐溫說：「我見識的人越多，我越喜歡我的狗。」（The more I know of Man, the more I like my dog.） 這個世界，貓狗的品格、尊嚴、生命價值，比一些人更高級。<br />\n保護波子，即是捍衛常理（Common Sense），如果香港還是一個文明社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780/1668934709845712/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780%2F1668934709845712%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=h%2BTfh%2Bc%2F8xBDxEFfhAUyC%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c9f083d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780/1668934709845712/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n陶傑係咪抽埋西方水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db5e456b1065664caa688d0b02b5f1a84390ecd","tid":431051,"uid":12070,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢保邊撚個波子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0abdcdc430238f13e486802a8a4e0d977c4f34","tid":431051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e1f88105c226e452c0331f393c503878574520","tid":431051,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8e27cd7bb14a50cdbf252ba9a47924efcfe3e8","tid":431051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0bf9ca539599434a6519b93c00d96842903519","tid":431051,"uid":10570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"So damn true"},{"pid":"9e2c9e06c0b3a2eda350e59156ce945dd00b5b40","tid":431051,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb70abc8ff10c8d0f2cc87a754faee269a48c2f","tid":431051,"uid":15880,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"貓真係你搞佢佢都廢事理你<br />\n<br />\n仲點會主動攻擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857f416f14544e393ad6079cb7d15ccee06a0215","tid":431051,"uid":70985,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓真係你搞佢佢都廢事理你<br />\n<br />\n仲點會主動攻擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蝗仔實係搞鳩人先啦，個老母就借啲意屈錢"},{"pid":"e36fe0a236287966cc315ee9b73599d9f1ce2d8f","tid":431051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"<im